  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shui's Odyssey is a narrative-driven puzzle game that tightly integrates storytelling and gameplay. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experience the passage of time for three generations</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will join the protagonist, \"Xiao Shui,\" on a profound journey to rediscover lost memories and embark on a soul-searching quest. Through  themes of love, family, and friendship, players will uncover emotional  chapters of life set against the backdrop of a significant era.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808960/extras/dac01b06beb1759c6f1d38eed8c1dce5.avif?t=1750910627\" width=600 height=312 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Imaginative visual puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the game unfolds, players will encounter a series of intricate visual illusions, akin to the unveiling of a scroll, gradually revealing the truth behind the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808960/extras/e624f5a2ff7faecafaba6c4cb47ac1a5.poster.avif?t=1750910627\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808960/extras/e624f5a2ff7faecafaba6c4cb47ac1a5.webm?t=1750910627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808960/extras/e624f5a2ff7faecafaba6c4cb47ac1a5.mp4?t=1750910627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Exquisite original hand-drawn illustrations</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring a wealth of delicate and stunning artwork and animations, a script inspired by real-life experiences, and meticulously designed gameplay mechanics, Shui's Odyssey offers a captivating gaming experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808960/extras/ce773257fc2f9d6d57e4d16df28c2a50.avif?t=1750910627\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shui's Odyssey is a narrative-driven puzzle game that tightly integrates storytelling and gameplay. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Experience the passage of time for three generations</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Players will join the protagonist, \"Xiao Shui,\" on a profound journey to rediscover lost memories and embark on a soul-searching quest. Through  themes of love, family, and friendship, players will uncover emotional  chapters of life set against the backdrop of a significant era.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808960/extras/dac01b06beb1759c6f1d38eed8c1dce5.avif?t=1750910627\" width=600 height=312 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Imaginative visual puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the game unfolds, players will encounter a series of intricate visual illusions, akin to the unveiling of a scroll, gradually revealing the truth behind the story.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808960/extras/e624f5a2ff7faecafaba6c4cb47ac1a5.poster.avif?t=1750910627\" width=600 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808960/extras/e624f5a2ff7faecafaba6c4cb47ac1a5.webm?t=1750910627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808960/extras/e624f5a2ff7faecafaba6c4cb47ac1a5.mp4?t=1750910627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Exquisite original hand-drawn illustrations</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Featuring a wealth of delicate and stunning artwork and animations, a script inspired by real-life experiences, and meticulously designed gameplay mechanics, Shui's Odyssey offers a captivating gaming experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2808960/extras/ce773257fc2f9d6d57e4d16df28c2a50.avif?t=1750910627\" width=600 height=300 /></span></p>",
